name: SURVIVE
description: She's a Balinese traditional dancer, for several years, there many art performances were staged in temple and tourism places, She and the local peoples are very happy because they can live from these art performances, but now, the pandemic has spread all over the world,  that makes the tourist places are closed,  art performances can't be held which makes traditional Balinese dancers struggle to survive without dance performances, but they still believe that the light will defeated the dark
